OL,3,CResident doctor strikes: How will it
OL,4,Cimpact the South West?
OL,6,FResident doctors across the South West
OL,7,Fwill strike for six days from tomorrow
OL,8,Fafter a long-running dispute over pay
OL,9,Fand jobs.
OL,11,FA national strike has been called by
OL,12,Fthe British Medical Association (BMA),
OL,13,Fwith Health Secretary, Wes Streeting
OL,14,Fbranding the move as "disappointing".
OL,16,FResident doctors - formerly known as
OL,17,Fjunior doctors - will remain on strike
OL,18,Funtil 7am on Monday 13 April.
OL,20,FWhich hospitals will be most impacted
OL,21,Fby the walk out?
OL,26,@vD@VOUvD@dO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
