OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1775555970
OL,3,CResident doctor strikes: How will it
OL,4,Cimpact the South West?
OL,6,FDuring the strike, people requiring
OL,7,Femergency care will have to travel to
OL,8,FGloucestershire Royal Hospital which
OL,9,Fis more than a half-hour drive away
OL,10,Ffrom Cheltenham.
OL,12,FNHS England's South West Medical
OL,13,FDirector, Dr Trevor Smith, said "We
OL,14,Fare deeply disappointed to be facing
OL,15,Fanother round of industrial action.
OL,17,F"Having been through several previous
OL,18,Frounds, we are well prepared and
OL,19,Fexperienced in responding to strike
OL,20,Faction.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1775555970
OL,3,CResident doctor strikes: How will it
OL,4,Cimpact the South West?
OL,6,F"The most important message is that
OL,7,Femergency care services remain open,
OL,8,Fif you have an emergency, please do
OL,9,Fcome forward.
OL,11,F"Those with urgent but non-emergency
OL,12,Fneeds should contact NHS 111, where
OL,13,Fthey can be directed to the most
OL,14,Fappropriate service."
OL,16,FWhy are the strikes going ahead?
OL,18,FThe strikes are pressing ahead after
OL,19,Fthe Government withdrew a key part of
OL,20,Fits offer to resident doctors.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1775555970
OL,3,CResident doctor strikes: How will it
OL,4,Cimpact the South West?
OL,6,FThe Department of Health and Social
OL,7,FCare confirmed last week that a
OL,8,Fproposed 1,000 extra training places
OL,9,Fwould no longer be "financially or
OL,10,Foperationally" possible, a move the
OL,11,FBMA says effectively scuppered a deal
OL,12,Fthat had been taking shape.
OL,14,FWes Streeting said: "It is
OL,15,Fdisappointing for patients and staff
OL,16,Falike that the BMA has decided to
OL,17,Fpress ahead with strikes this week,
OL,18,Fdespite the deal we put to them which
OL,19,Fwould have seen resident doctors 35.2%
OL,20,Fbetter off, on average, than they were
OL,21,Ffour years ago."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1775555970
OL,3,CResident doctor strikes: How will it
OL,4,Cimpact the South West?
OL,6,FHowever, Dr Jack Fletcher, chairman of
OL,7,Fthe BMA's resident doctors committee,
OL,8,Fpushed back, saying the Health
OL,9,FSecretary was "failing to acknowledge
OL,10,Fa deal was taking shape until his
OL,11,FGovernment quietly watered it down."
OL,13,FHe added that resident doctors were
OL,14,F"as keen as he is to bring an end to
OL,15,Fthe strikes," but said the Government
OL,16,Fneeded to stop "using our next
OL,17,Fgeneration of consultants as a
OL,18,Fbargaining chip."
OL,20,FWhat should patients do?
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1775555970
OL,3,CResident doctor strikes: How will it
OL,4,Cimpact the South West?
OL,6,FProfessor Ramani Moonesinghe, National
OL,7,FClinical Director for Critical and
OL,8,FPreoperative Care at NHS England,
OL,9,Freassured patients across the country,
OL,10,Fincluding those in the South West,
OL,11,Fthat the health service would remain
OL,12,Fopen throughout the strike.
OL,14,F"Staff across the NHS will be doing
OL,15,Feverything they can this week to keep
OL,16,Fpatients safe and ensure people can
OL,17,Fcontinue to get the care they need,"
OL,18,Fshe said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1775555970
OL,3,CResident doctor strikes: How will it
OL,4,Cimpact the South West?
OL,6,F"Patients should come forward as
OL,7,Fnormal and attend any appointments
OL,8,Funless they are contacted otherwise.
OL,9,FPlease call 999 or come to A&E in an
OL,10,Femergency, and use 111 online first if
OL,11,Fyou need urgent but not life-
OL,12,Fthreatening help.
OL,14,FDuring December's strikes, the NHS
OL,15,Fdelivered almost 95% of planned
OL,16,Factivity nationally, though Dr
OL,17,FFletcher cautioned that many senior
OL,18,Fdoctors covering for striking
OL,19,Fcolleagues were "exhausted and
OL,20,Fdemoralised."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1775555970
OL,3,CResident doctor strikes: How will it
OL,4,Cimpact the South West?
OL,6,FThe BMA said it remained willing to
OL,7,Freach a settlement. "We are willing to
OL,8,Fbring an end to industrial action," Dr
OL,9,FFletcher said, "but we are not seeing
OL,10,Fthat willingness from Government so
OL,11,Ffar."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
